based in Bartlesville, Oklahoma, the United States.
</P>
<P>
The agreement was signed on the sidelines of the Middle East
and North Africa Economic Conference which was opened here
today. Host Qatar is presenting some 70 projects to some 850
foreign investors and businessmen who are attending the
conference. 
