during the meeting that the Swiss government will encourage Swiss
investors to make more investments in Thailand.
</P>
<P>
Switzerland is Thailand's 19th largest trading partner. Last
year, bilateral trade totaled 195.7 million U.S. dollars, with
Thailand suffering a trade deficit of about 509 million dollars.
